role_description: An Ansible role that install Xcode on macOS
role_description_full_overview: [Xcode](https://developer.apple.com/xcode/) is Apple's integrated development environment for macOS, used to develop software for macOS, iOS, iPadOS, watchOS, and tvOS.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that install Xcode on macOS.
